>{{note|1}} All housemates downstairs won immunity because one housemate from there was already evicted, to equilibrate the numbers.\n* {{note|2}} By default, everyone faced the public vote.\n* {{note|3}} Housemates nominated face-to-face. Housemates was only allowed to nominate within each team. The housemates of either team with the most votes face the public vote.\n* {{note|4}} The housemate with the most nominations had to choose with whom he or she would face the public vote.\n* {{note|5}} Housemates are allowed to nominate themselves. Every housemate with at least one nomination faces the public vote.</small>\n{{refend}}\n\n=== Nominations: Results ===\n\n==Ratings<ref name=\"Quotenmeter\">{{cite web|title=German television ratings|work=Quotenmeter.de|url=http://www.quotenmeter.de/|accessdate=2009-03-28}}</ref><ref name=\"DWDL\">{{cite web|title=German television ratings|work=DWDL.de|url=http://www.dwdl.de/|accessdate=2009-03-28}}</ref>==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! align=\"center\" rowspan=2|Episode\n! align=\"center\" colspan=2|from 3 years\n! align=\"center\" colspan=2|14- to 49-year-old\n|-\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"|Viewers<br>(in millions)\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"|Share<br>(in %)\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"|Viewers<br>(in millions)\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"|Share<br>(in %)\n|-\n|1\n|3.16\n|12.2\n|1.79\n|18.9\n|-\n|2\n|2.84\n|13.5\n|1.61\n|19.6\n|-\n|3\n|2.67\n|12.4\n|1.44\n|17.5\n|-\n|4\n|2.62\n|12.9\n|1.27\n|15.7\n|-\n|5\n|2.88\n|15.2\n|1.52\n|18.9\n|-\n|6\n|2.72\n|15.4\n|1.41\n|18.6\n|-\n|7\n|3.14\n|17.7\n|1.68\n|22.4\n|-\n|8\n|3.01\n|11.4\n|1.57\n|16.0\n|-\n|9\n|3.02\n|14.3\n|1.62\n|19.4\n|-\n|10\n|2.78\n|14.7\n|1.49\n|18.1\n|-\n|11\n|2.80\n|15.6\n|1.44\n|19.1\n|-\n|12\n|2.87\n|16.0\n|1.46\n|19.9\n|-\n|13\n|2.86\n|15.8\n|1.44\n|19.0\n|-\n|14\n|2.88\n|15.1\n|1.54\n|19.4\n|-\n|15\n|3.03\n|12.3\n|1.64\n|19.4\n|-\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.sat1.de/tv/promi-big